Recommends: genesis-world-assets
# NOTE: We deliberately do NOT Recommend nvidia-driver-* here. Inside
# Docker / dev containers the host driver is injected by the NVIDIA
# Container Toolkit and pulling a driver deb fails on overlay-fs with
# "Invalid cross-device link". On bare-metal hosts users install the
# driver from their own apt source. Either way, recommending it does
# more harm than good.
Description: Genesis physics simulator (vendored Python environment)
 Genesis is a GPU-accelerated physics engine and rendering platform for
 robotics and embodied-AI research. This package ships a self-contained
 Python virtual environment under /opt/genesis/venv, containing torch,
 taichi, and the genesis-world engine pinned to the packaged git revision.
 A thin wrapper /usr/bin/genesis launches the vendored interpreter.
